  "Every gradient function needs two color at least, and then can set a percentage at this color. Here are two main type: <strong>linear</strong> and <strong>radial</strong>. One is gradient from edge, and another is from center. You can check whether browsers support this property from <a href='http://caniuse.com/#search=gradient' class='link'>here</a>.",
  "",
  "Example 1:",
